		img(src='/images/logo.svg', width='160')
		h1 KeystoneJS by Morten and Anders
		p You are looking at a <strong>Christmas Site</strong> right now. This is a website about Christmas.
		p The <strong>frontend</strong> is built with <strong>PUG</strong> and bootstrap
